dc_title_s: Roads and ROW: Kewaunee County, Wisconsin, 2020
dct_alternativeTitle_sm: Roads and ROW Kewaunee County, WI 2020
dc_description_s: This data represents roads and Right Of Ways (ROW) for Kewaunee County, Wisconsin in 2020. For Roads: [Roads data of Juneau County were initially created using the US Census TIGER file. They were then reprojected to Juneau County coordinates. Edits by the Juneau County Land Information Office for the addition of new roads were done. 2003 & 2010 aerial photographs and new survey maps were used to help with the edits.]
